snippet.title: F1 2018 | MAKE HEADLINES | Paul Ricard Reveal [UK]
snippet.description:
Prepare for the French Grand Prix​ with F1® 2018 - let Pierre Gasly​, Romain Grosjean​, Esteban Ocon​ and Carlos Sainz​ take you around the Circuit Paul Ricard​.
